# Windsurf Rules for auditjayagent

## What This Repo Is
A library of smart contract security audit skills for elite-level Solidity auditing.

## How to Run the Audit Agent
The skill entry point is: `audit-agent/SKILL.md`

Trigger keywords: "audit", "run audit agent", "security review", "find bugs", "check for vulnerabilities"

Install command (for target codebases):
```
Install https://github.com/jayjoshix/audit-skills and run audit agent on the codebase
```

## Output Rules (Hard Constraints)
- Never fabricate findings — every claim must trace to actual source code
- Apply Gates A–F from `audit-agent/references/shared-rules.md` to ALL findings
- Output format: CONFIRMED / PROBABLE / HYPOTHESIS only
- Auto-discard: findings requiring privileged roles (owner, admin, deployer) with no escalation path
- Auto-merge: same root cause with different attack paths → keep the most complete path only
